'''羅伯特·格倫·瑞伊'''（{{lang-en|Robert Glenn Ray}}，{{bd|1991年|10月1日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前效力於西雅圖水手。他先前曾效力過老虎、響尾蛇與藍鳥等隊，他在2017年曾入選過一次明星賽。
==職業生涯==
===華盛頓國民===
[[2010年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2010年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，國民隊在第12輪選進瑞伊。而他最後用79萬9000美元的簽約金成功加盟國民隊。<ref>{{cite news |last=Kilgore |first=Adam |url=http://voices.washingtonpost.com/nationalsjournal/2010/08/nationals_announce_signing_of.html |title=Nationals announce signing of Robbie Ray |work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |date=August 16, 2010 |access-date=December 2, 2013 |archive-date=2013-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130226142859/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/nationalsjournal/2010/08/nationals_announce_signing_of.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他先在短期1A出賽1場比賽，之後在2011年升上1A。那年他拿下2勝3敗，防禦率3.13。<ref>{{cite news |last=Sheinin |first=Dave |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/nationals-journal/post/a-dazzling-debut-for-hagerstowns-robbie-ray/2011/05/10/AF5mjyhG_blog.html |title=A dazzling debut for Hagerstown's Robbie Ray |newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |date=May 10, 2011 |access-date=December 2, 2013 |archive-date=2019-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410020459/https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/nationals-journal/post/a-dazzling-debut-for-hagerstowns-robbie-ray/2011/05/10/AF5mjyhG_blog.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2012年，瑞伊升上高階1A。不過他僅拿下4勝12敗，防禦率6.56。<ref>{{cite web |last=Seiner |first=Jake |url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130606&content_id=49767492&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb |title=Ray continues to rebound for Nats |publisher=[[Minor_League_Baseball|Minor League Baseball]] |date=January 2, 2013 |access-date=December 2, 2013 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220182938/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20130606&content_id=49767492&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在高階1A又待了一年，<ref>{{cite news |last=Kilgore |first=Adam |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/nationals-journal/wp/2013/05/02/a-j-cole-robbie-ray-together-again-at-potomac/ |title=A. J. Cole, Robbie Ray together again at Potomac |newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |date=May 2, 2013 |access-date=December 2, 2013 |archive-date=2014-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205121211/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/nationals-journal/wp/2013/05/02/a-j-cole-robbie-ray-together-again-at-potomac/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>投出6勝3敗後成功升上2A。<ref>{{cite journal |first=Geoff |last=Morrow |url=http://www.pennlive.com/senators/index.ssf/2013/07/robbie_ray_makes_double-a_debu.html |title=Robbie Ray makes Double-A debut for Harrisburg Senators in opener of Friday night doubleheader on City Island |newspaper=[[The_Patriot_News|The Patriot News]] |date=July 5, 2013 |access-date=April 30, 2014 |journal= |archive-date=2018-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181227085227/https://www.pennlive.com/senators/index.ssf/2013/07/robbie_ray_makes_double-a_debu.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===底特律老虎===
2013年12月2日，國民隊用瑞伊、Ian Krol和Steve Lombardozzi Jr.跟老虎隊交易[[道格·費斯特|道格·費斯特]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://detroit.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/det/detroit-tigers-trade-doug-fister-to-washington-nationals-for-three-players?ymd=20131202&content_id=64343036&vkey=news_det |title=Tigers send Fister to Nats for three players |publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]] |first=Jason |last=Beck |date=December 2, 2013 |access-date=December 3, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131206034225/http://detroit.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/det/detroit-tigers-trade-doug-fister-to-washington-nationals-for-three-players?ymd=20131202&content_id=64343036&vkey=news_det |archive-date=December 6, 2013 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.freep.com/article/20140216/SPORTS02/302160082/detroit-tigers-robbie-ray-doug-fister |title=He may be key to Doug Fister deal, but lefty Robbie Ray knows he must prove himself to Detroit Tigers |first=George |last=Sipple |newspaper=[[Detroit_Free_Press|Detroit Free Press]] |date=February 16, 2014 |access-date=April 30, 2014 |journal= |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924132835/http://www.freep.com/article/20140216/SPORTS02/302160082/detroit-tigers-robbie-ray-doug-fister |dead-url=no }}</ref>2014年，瑞伊從3A開季。4月26日，由於隊上投手Aníbal Sánchez受傷，因此瑞伊被拉上大聯盟，並在5月6日完成大聯盟初登板。他在初登板便拿下大聯盟首勝，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/gametracker/recap/MLB_20140506_HOU@DET |title=Tigers 11, Astros 4 |work=[[CBS_Sports|CBS Sports]] |date=May 6, 2014 |access-date=May 16, 2014 |archive-date=2021-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224141935/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/gametracker/recap/MLB_20140506_HOU@DET/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>後來又回到小聯盟。8月12日，因為Sánchez再次受傷，瑞伊又一次登上大聯盟。不過這次他主投5局失4分吞下敗投。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.mlive.com/tigers/index.ssf/2014/08/tigers_pirates_robbie_ray.html | title = Pirates 4, Tigers 2: Robbie Ray takes loss, bats silent as Detroit losing streak reaches four games | publisher = [[MLive|MLive]] | first = Chris | last = Iott | date = August 12, 2014 | access-date = August 12, 2014 | archive-date = 2018-09-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180910054306/https://www.mlive.com/tigers/index.ssf/2014/08/tigers_pirates_robbie_ray.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>
===亞利桑那響尾蛇===
2014年12月5日，響尾蛇、老虎和洋基發動三方交易，老虎隊將瑞伊和Domingo Leyba交易到響尾蛇隊；響尾蛇隊將[[狄迪·葛雷格里斯|狄迪·葛雷格里斯]]送往洋基；老虎從洋基得到Shane Greene。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/103253536/didi-gregorius-goes-to-yankees-in-three-team-trade | title = Gregorius goes to Yanks, Ray to Arizona, Greene to Tigers | publisher = [[Major_League_Baseball|MLB]] | first = Joey | last = Nowak | date = December 5, 2014 | access-date = December 5, 2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141210171036/http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/103253536/didi-gregorius-goes-to-yankees-in-three-team-trade | archive-date = December 10, 2014 }}</ref>

2015年，瑞伊從3A出發，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.kolotv.com/sports/headlines/Diamondbacks-Make-4-Roster-Moves-After-Final-Spring-Game-298688391.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-17 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084112/http://www.kolotv.com/sports/headlines/Diamondbacks-Make-4-Roster-Moves-After-Final-Spring-Game-298688391.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>並在季中面對洛磯隊的雙重賽中登板。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/gametracker/recap/MLB_20150506_ARI@COL_2 |title=Gregorius Diamondbacks earn 1st DH sweep on road since 2006 |publisher=cbssports.com |first=Pat |last=Graham |date=May 6, 2015 |access-date=July 7, 2015 |archive-date=2019-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190409102610/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/gametracker/recap/MLB_20150506_ARI@COL_2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年6月7日，瑞伊敲出大聯盟首轟。不過他這年僅拿下8勝15敗，防禦率4.90。被打擊率高達3成52為大聯盟最高。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=8&season=2015&month=0&season1=2015&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=12,d |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2015 » Pitchers » Dashboard | FanGraphs Baseball |publisher=Fangraphs.com |access-date=2019-12-21 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225031037/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=8&season=2015&month=0&season1=2015&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=12,d |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年球季初，瑞伊的表現相當糟糕。他在球季前8場先發防禦率高達4.57，不過到後面他完全像變了個人似的，接下來8場先發投出6勝1敗，防禦率僅1.81。5月30日，他投出了生涯首場完封勝。隨後5場先發他更是全數拿下勝投，防禦率低到只有0.24。因此他也成功入選明星賽。7月28日，瑞伊在先發面對紅雀隊時遭到[[盧克·沃伊特|盧克·沃伊特]]的強襲球擊中頭部。雖然他頭部縫了5針，不過所幸沒有造成腦震盪。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.azcentral.com/story/sports/mlb/diamondbacks/2017/07/29/robbie-ray-diamondbacks-pitcher-hit-head/522144001/|title=Robbie Ray hit in head by line drive, knocked out of loss to Cardinals|newspaper=azcentral.com|first=Nick|last=Piecoro|date=July 28, 2017|access-date=August 11, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.azcentral.com/story/sports/mlb/diamondbacks/2017/07/30/diamondbacks-lineup-dbacks-pitching-walker-cardinals/523617001/|title=Robbie Ray thankful head injury wasn't worse|newspaper=azcentral.com|first=Nick|last=Piecoro|date=July 30, 2017|access-date=August 11, 2018}}</ref>9月4日，他面對道奇隊投出生涯新高的單場14次三振。最後他在這年拿下15勝5敗，防禦率2.89。他的K9值(平均每9局投球能送出的三振數)高達12.11，被打擊率僅有1成99。儘管他的保送率和被擊球強勁率都是大聯盟最高，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=2&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=20,d |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2017 » Pitchers » Batted Ball Statistics | FanGraphs Baseball |publisher=Fangraphs.com |access-date=2019-12-21 |archive-date=2019-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521201747/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=2&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=20,d |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=8&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=10,d |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2017 » Pitchers » Dashboard | FanGraphs Baseball |publisher=Fangraphs.com |access-date=2019-12-21 |archive-date=2019-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521215449/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=8&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=10,d |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過他的被擊球率也是大聯盟最低。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=5&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=8,a |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2017 » Pitchers » Plate Discipline Statistics | FanGraphs Baseball |publisher=Fangraphs.com |access-date=2019-12-21 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804201500/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=5&season=2017&month=0&season1=2017&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=8,a |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2018年，瑞伊成為響尾蛇隊的2號先發，不過他在4月30日因為斜肌受傷而進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.azcentral.com/story/sports/mlb/diamondbacks/2018/04/30/arizona-diamondbacks-robbie-ray-disabled-list-oblique-strain/567158002/ |title=Arizona Diamondbacks news: Robbie Ray heads to DL with oblique strain |publisher=Azcentral.com |date=2018-04-30 |access-date=2019-12-21}}</ref>整年他投出6勝2敗，防禦率3.93。

2019年，瑞伊寫下了生涯新高的33場先發。不過他每場先發平均投不超過5局，最後他拿下12勝8敗，防禦率4.34，並投出生涯新高的235次三振。

2020年8月16日，瑞伊投出大聯盟生涯1000次三振。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.mlb.com/dbacks/news/robbie-ray-hits-1-000-strikeout-milestone | title=Escobar, Ray break out as D-backs sweep | work=MLB.com | author=Steve Gilbert | date=August 16, 2020 | access-date=August 19, 2020 | archive-date=2021-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410012040/https://www.mlb.com/dbacks/news/robbie-ray-hits-1-000-strikeout-milestone | dead-url=no }}</ref>這年他在響尾蛇僅投出1勝4敗，防禦率7.84。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/rayro02.shtml|title=Robbie Ray Stats|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2021-03-17|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502222404/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/rayro02.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>並投出國聯最多的31次保送。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/NL/2020-pitching-leaders.shtml|title=2020 National League Pitching Leaders|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2021-03-17|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325151631/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/NL/2020-pitching-leaders.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===多倫多藍鳥===
2020年8月31日，響尾蛇用瑞伊向藍鳥交易Travis Bergen。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/bluejays/news/robbie-ray-deal-to-blue-jays|title=Toronto acquires Ray (official), Villar (source)|last=Matheson|first=Keegan|work=MLB.com|date=August 31, 2020|access-date=August 31, 2020|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107215457/https://www.mlb.com/bluejays/news/robbie-ray-deal-to-blue-jays|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月1日，瑞伊完成他在藍鳥隊的初登板。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.mlb.com/bluejays/news/robbie-ray-makes-blue-jays-debut-in-loss | title=Ray shows potential in Blue Jays debut | work=MLB.com | author=Keegan Matheson | date=September 1, 2020 | access-date=September 2, 2020 | archive-date=2020-09-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903161820/https://www.mlb.com/bluejays/news/robbie-ray-makes-blue-jays-debut-in-loss | dead-url=no }}</ref>這年他在藍鳥隊共出賽5場比賽，拿下1勝1敗，防禦率4.79。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/player/robbie-ray-592662?stats=career-r-pitching-mlb&year=2020|title=Robbie Ray Stats, Fantasy & News|website=MLB.com|access-date=December 1, 2020}}</ref>2021年，他和球隊簽下1年800萬美元的合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sportsnet.ca/mlb/article/report-blue-jays-reach-agreement-robbie-ray-one-year-8m-deal/|title=Blue Jays reach agreement with Robbie Ray on one-year, $8M deal|date=November 7, 2020|work=[[Sportsnet|Sportsnet]]|access-date=2021-03-17|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121135433/https://www.sportsnet.ca/mlb/article/report-blue-jays-reach-agreement-robbie-ray-one-year-8m-deal/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年，瑞伊拿下13勝7敗，防禦率2.84，送出248次三振。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=8&season=2021&month=0&season1=2021&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&startdate=2021-01-01&enddate=2021-12-31&sort=13,d |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-11-30 |archive-date=2021-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019022335/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=8&season=2021&month=0&season1=2021&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&startdate=2021-01-01&enddate=2021-12-31&sort=13,d |dead-url=no }}</ref>他不僅成功拿下美聯防禦率王和美聯三振王，還差點以全票通過的方式拿下美聯賽揚獎。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2021/11/17/robbie-ray-al-cy-young-award-2021-toronto-blue-jays/8650938002/|title=Blue Jays lefty Robbie Ray wins American League Cy Young Award|first=Jesse|last=Yomtov|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=November 17, 2021|accessdate=November 18, 2021|archive-date=2021-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211203105140/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2021/11/17/robbie-ray-al-cy-young-award-2021-toronto-blue-jays/8650938002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
